Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' for cases involving 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and activity Completed + In Call for cases where activity Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum time for 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' grouped by 'country'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases with 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to be followed by 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total time it takes from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases that also include 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in variants leading to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in variants where 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' follows
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation occurs

Name: Minimum time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' occurs
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in variants that do not lead to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before reaching 'Completed + Closed' without 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in variants with multiple 'Accepted + In Progress' occurrences before 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
